OL,4,BMarco Silva: Everton manager facing
OL,5,Bpivotal match against West Ham
OL,6, When Marco Silva described Everton's
OL,7, meeting with West Ham United as "must
OL,8, win", he was not simply trotting out a
OL,9, cliche - he was hoisting a warning flag
OL,10, for his own perilous position.
OL,12,FThe 42-year-old Portuguese is under
OL,13,Fmounting pressure after a run of four
OL,14,FPremier League defeats plunged a club
OL,15,Fwith top-four ambitions into the
OL,16,Frelegation places.
OL,19,FNot necessarily - as there is a genuine
OL,20,Fdesire at Everton to give Silva every
OL,21,Fchance to succeed.
